WEBVTT

00:03:58.800 --> 00:04:05.176
we hand over reading and writing
to children with sole aim of success.

00:04:05.200 --> 00:04:11.696
There on, there is an addiction
to run this rat race of success.

00:04:11.720 --> 00:04:15.656
Keeping happiness on the back
burner becomes a habit.

00:04:15.680 --> 00:04:20.255
Even if they manage to make
a successful career,

00:04:20.279 --> 00:04:22.936
happiness still eludes them.

00:04:22.960 --> 00:04:27.936
I did not agree with this idea of success.

00:04:27.960 --> 00:04:31.816
Whether it is studies or life,